plans.name: Annual
plans.description: Annual Plan is for 365 days from commencement and provides  low cost access to Bikes for as little as 18 cents per day.

plans.name: Pay-As-You-Ride
plans.description: PAYR provides a flexible 365 day plan for accessing Bikes when you need them. After payment of the Membership Fee, you are only charged when you use the Bikes.
